{
  "text": "When multi-stage training was performed, the learning rate values were chosen using hyper parameter search for each stage of the training to optimize the results. Their values in pretrainings were higher then the one found for the final training. This is also in accordance with neuroscience studies [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "23391239"
